title: I got the Riot Kayle skin, but didn't received the poro icon

replies.body: Yea im the same but the opposite,i didn't receive riot kayle but i got poro.I really am looking forward to main kayle once again.

We are still rolling these out to a lot of eligible accounts, and you may not get everything all at once.  Bookmark our current [support ticker ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-)for updates as we process out the gifts.  Let me know if you have any questions.
